<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wie ewch Hanns Teczel ewr
                        ratgesell fürbracht hab, daz im <expan>lantman<ex>n</ex>s</expan> weise
                                <expan>fürkome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz im <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Höhel, des <expan cert="unknown">F<ex>ricz</ex></expan>
                        Höhels <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan>, dröwe
                            <expan>zuzugreiff<ex>en</ex></expan>, als von
                            <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan cert="unknown">F<ex>ricz</ex></expan> Höhels weibs
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan cert="unknown">F<ex>ricz</ex></expan> Höhel für uns besant und
                        fleissig <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zurede gesaczt. Der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, daz er niht wisse, daz sein
                                <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> dem
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Teczel icht gedröwt hab
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dröwe. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                        <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
